snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk in Chile together
snippet.description:
PICTURED: Amber Heard and Elon Musk enjoy festive trip to Chile together as on-again couple are pictured having dinner with pals.
Amber Heard and Elon Musk are enjoying a festive getaway to Chile together.

The 31-year-old actress and the Tesla CEO began dating in 2016 before parting ways in August this year, and although they recently denied a reconciliation, the pair have been spotted vacationing together in South America.

In a photo obtained by Dailymail.com the reunited couple are seen dining with family - including Elon's brother Kimbal - and friends near Santiago, Chile.

The picture was shared by an Instagram account named El Taringa and shows Amber in a black dress and tan wide-brim fedora gazing down at her phone.
